Title: Travelers
Plot: In 1990 Agent Fox Mulder visits an aging FBI Agent named Arthur Dales. He listens to a story of the agents assigned to a would-be X-File in the Cold War era of the 1950's and how Mulder's father was connected to a series of strange deaths.
GuestStars: Fredric Lehne, Garret Dillahunt, Brian Leckner, David Moreland, Eileen Pedde, Dean Aylesworth, David Fredericks, Mitchell Kosterman, Roger Haskett, Jane Perry, J. Douglas Stewart, Cory Dagg, Eric W. Gilder, Darren
